How to Install Sass

Step 1
I installed Node version 20.16 on my machine by downloading it on the official node website

Step 2
Confirm Node installation by running node -V command on the command line. Should output the installed node version.

Step 3
I installed sass using the npm package by running the command npm install -g sass on the command line.

Step 4
Confirm the node version installed by running the command sass ---version on the terminal.
